Found it! The timezone mismatch: `datetime.now(timezone.utc)` stores UTC date (March 30) but `date.today()` returns local JST date (March 31). The streak calculation compares UTC dates against local dates.

The fix: use local time for `last_reviewed` since streak should be based on user's local day:

● Edit vocabulary.py +1 -1
  └ app/dal/vocabulary.py

